# AWS DevOps Project

This is my first project to deploy a website on AWS EC2.  

## Tools Used
- AWS EC2 (Free Tier)
- Linux
- Apache web server
- GitHub

## Steps Followed
1. Created simple HTML website (index.html)
2. Created AWS EC2 server
3. Installed Apache server on Linux
4. Uploaded index.html to EC2
5. Tested website in browser
